data.description: Motivated Seller! Assumable VA Loan at 5%. House comes with near 6 figures of post-build improvements.This beautiful home design features a private attached suite with a living room, kitchenette, bedroom and bathroom, ideal for multigenerational households. Main floor has an open floor plan with a custom-built gas fireplace in the living room, quartz countertops, stainless appliances and corner pantry in the kitchen with a large center island. Upstairs features four bedrooms including a large master suite with a bath and walk-in closet. Exterior backyard landscaping completed with custom stone walkway and patio with pergola. 3-car tandem garage. Full size unfinished basement.
